==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: kangaroos-foot
<hw>kangaroo's-foot</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A sedgelike spring-flowering
herb (<spn>Anigozanthus manglesii</spn>) of Australia, having clustered
flowers covered with woolly hairs.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> kangaroo paw, kangaroo-foot plant, Australian sword
lily, <spn>Anigozanthus manglesii</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kansan</ent>⟦br⟧
